      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows some age-related wear, including minor paint fading on the hood and a few small door dings, but it remains structurally sound. Inside, the upholstery is clean but shows typical signs of use on the driver\u2019s seat and floor mats. Mechanically, it starts and runs smoothly, though it will likely need new tires within the next year. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone who prioritizes utility over a perfect cosmetic appearance.",
