    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a vehicle; it's a time machine carved from chrome and dreams. Bathed in a deep, liquid finish that catches the sunset like a fine vintage, this beauty commands every street corner it graces. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of artisan craftsmanship, where the scent of rich, supple leather transports you to a more elegant era. Every curve of its sculpted body tells a story of speed and sophistication, waiting for a new pilot to write the next chapter. To drive it is to feel the heartbeat of automotive history beneath your fingertips\u2014a rare opportunity to own a masterpiece that looks as though it just rolled off the showroom floor.",
      "price": 46500.0,
